Data Insights Interface

Learn how to navigate insights and become familiar with the user interface.

Insight Summary Panels display a summation of model variables. Each variable insight consists of sensitive field badge, insight title, insight chart, version update, and bookmark insight.

Variables Panel lists fields you are analyzing, with a search box, filter for sensitive fields, and importance ranking. Filter selector allows surface insights by variable or value.

Einstein Discovery stories are now models. Predict & Improve Outcomes. Decision Optimization (Beta).
